data.text:
Saiyuki Reload Gunlock is another role-playing video game and was released by Bandai for the PlayStation2.

Information[]

This fighting game features a total of eight playable characters including Sanzo, Goku, Gojyo and Hakkai as well as Kougaiji, Chin Yisou, Kamisama, and Hazel. Playable game modes include traditional single and multiplayer modes, as well as Practice Mode, Watch Mode, and a story-akin Dramatic Mode.

- Wikipedia
